room to work here.

308
00:17:00,434 --> 00:17:01,679
Oh, no! No!

309
00:17:01,894 --> 00:17:03,223
- Pulmonary embolus?
- Probably.

310
00:17:03,438 --> 00:17:06,393
- Repeat a gas,.5 atropine.
