Multiple lacs to the chest and back.

403
00:22:23,224 --> 00:22:25,384
BP's 70/30. Pulse thready at 144.

404
00:22:25,603 --> 00:22:26,884
Sir, are you with us?

405
00:22:27,105 --> 00:22:28,435
- Peter?
- I'm on my way home.

406
00:22:28,650 --> 00:22:31,522
- Very funny.
